Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:03:59.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs65}註：豆芽男是日本歌手「__」(下劃線)創作的作品或角色。內心柔弱的「食草系」男性。\N稱自己不是豆芽男而是松坂牛（日本三大和牛之一），\N發誓最終會成為「將你燃燒的豆芽男」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:03:59.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為會不會全是豆芽男
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:07.23,qianxu-huamian3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&HFBF4F3&\3c&HD8CBCB&\pos(500,762)\b1}本內迪托
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:02.41,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:07.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這國家居然還會有比我故鄉更炎熱的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.07,0:04:16.17,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？比想像中的要過激…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:17.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟海外遊戲不同意義上的過激
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:21.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種東西在便利店出售沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:30.96,qianxu-huamian3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad1\bord1\fs50\frz269.1\c&HD4CBC3&\3c&H503827&\move(452,478,458,998)}{\fn@方正细圆_GBK\3c&HD2C9C1&\4c&H533723&}冷酷的謎之男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:30.96,qianxu-huamian3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\fn@方正细圆_GBK\c&HD0C8C2&\3c&HDFD5CF&\frz268.8\move(148,588,146,1124)}我 對地獄以外一概不知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:24.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我 對地獄以外一概不知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:27.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這位老爺爺 感覺給人一種老練暗殺者的氛圍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:29.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種纖細的線條的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:34.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道這位老爺爺是…不不不怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:34.38,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord1\frz272.1\pos(1498,450)}{\fn@方正大黑_GBK\c&H1D1F41&\3c&H57616C&}撲通…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:34.38,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord1\frz270.3\pos(104,452)}{\fn@方正大黑_GBK\c&H1D1F41&\3c&H57616C&}撲通撲通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:35.87,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,極樂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.47,0:04:39.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…極樂世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:52.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,手頭裡有…750日元嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:54.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:55.94,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:59.07,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是承認了自己還是不夠了解 類似這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西需要稍後仔細調查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.59,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把它作為資料放在身邊而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:07.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,背後的廣告也挺過激的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:11.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有條形碼所以必須拿給收銀員看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:13.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正不認識 隨便…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天天氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:16.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:17.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:22.75,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安藤先生？他在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:24.91,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,換兼職了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:28.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 會不會兼任報紙派發員？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:26.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:31.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想自己的興趣被誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這本書現在不買也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:37.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給商品造成損壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:39.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在剛才滑行的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:43.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須得買了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:46.27,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 店裡有的東西買了有什麼不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有必要去在意…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:51.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是太難為情了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:55.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 我是核心向玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:57.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎麼回事這色色的廣告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:06:00.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這本書又必須得買
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:03.65,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 反正只要安全通過收銀台就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:05.07,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偽裝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:08.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自古以來 男學生在買黃書的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:11.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用正經的書夾著掩藏自己的好色之心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:16.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在上面放一本「JUM○」 只露出條形碼的話 也許…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:19.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 去買「JUM○」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:24.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不行 買了BL雜誌就只剩210日元了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:25.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不夠錢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:30.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易也解除了安藤先生的誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:35.99,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 比起混混 被認為是軟派玩家在感情上更讓人不快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能把書露出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:40.30,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5\fs60\3c&H9B7033&\c&HF5F6F4&\pos(794,548)\b0}請自由領取
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:40.30,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord5\fs70\c&H10A4E9&\3c&H64897A&\b1\pos(796,766)}考取駕駛執照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:42.03,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5\fs80\3c&H9B7033&\c&HF5F6F4&\pos(906,444)\b0}請自由領取
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:45.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.31,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,換兼職了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:50.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是三谷裳嗎 好久不見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:55.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 每週的這天是便利店兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:58.47,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:01.59,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來只要這偽裝戰術能順利發揮…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:02.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:04.31,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這雜誌…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,免費的不是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個不是駕校的小冊子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:10.88,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\shad0\bord5\fs70\c&H10A4E9&\3c&H64897A&\b1\pos(434,266)}考取駕駛執照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:10.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高一就考駕照的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:13.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是摩托駕照對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:19.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不全露光了嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那那那那個…那…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:25.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 竟然會瞄準這本隨便拿的雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:31.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前段時間坐安藤先生的摩托的時候 感覺非常痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三…三谷裳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:36.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…這種事應該由作為男人的我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:43.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 有什麼推薦的駕校 告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:45.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:47.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:51.47,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣…安藤先生的視野就被封鎖住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:54.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這個色情廣告要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:00.41,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 把這個收銀台的這個巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:01.81,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拿兩個！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:04.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把色情…消除！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:06.27,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:11.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 感覺好像反而更色情了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:12.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加上男人穿著色情泳裝的違和感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:17.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像被強調了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:18.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是立體的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:20.71,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord1\fs300\fn@思源宋体 CN Medium\frz269.8\b1\3c&HFEFEFE&\pos(1328,384)}這樣不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.90,qianxu-zhengwen,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\bord1\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1442,638)}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.57,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話還是拿走更…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:24.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說 還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這下怎麼樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:38.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能看見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像穿著巧克力吊帶背心一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:43.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,色氣 完全消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:45.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個來決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:47.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:49.71,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為看起來好像要花很久時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:50.71,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.11,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的郵箱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:54.11,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是找到了好地方的話就告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:54.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,驚！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:57.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:08:59.99,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我要去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:01.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩結下賬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:03.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:09.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雜誌…一本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:11.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和…零食嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:12.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個也加上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:15.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總共15個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:18.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,15個 和…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:20.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 錢在這
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:23.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 先找您錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,袋子就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:26.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就那樣 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:31.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 啊 三谷裳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:32.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:34.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一邊去上學一邊看的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成了 成了 成了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:37.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完美地矇混過關啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,任務完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:41.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就是出門之後放進包裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:42.91,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 三谷裳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:44.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:45.39,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:48.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,郵箱地址的這裡是BL還是LOL？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是BL
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.78,0:09:51.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三谷裳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:55.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫「Boy’s Love」來著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:58.59,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:09:59.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:02.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要毫不遮掩地拿著走比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:05.87,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別搞錯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有打算否定你的興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:10.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那個雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有點給人色情的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:18.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對這種東西抱有偏見的人也是有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:21.27,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 邊走邊看書也很危險哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然說不定是我多管閒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:27.39,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我是在擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:29.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:30.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:32.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:35.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們店也有紙袋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:36.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:37.47,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這下就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:39.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:41.19,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等不到放學後什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:42.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三谷裳你真是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:43.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:46.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:51.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 千緒 那一堆巧克力是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:53.07,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你的飯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:56.51,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 別嘲諷別人的興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:03.11,qianxu-cut,NTP,0,0,0,,{\xshad5\yshad5\bord3\fs120\c&H8800E1&\3c&HFEFFFE&\4c&HFCFF9C&\b1\pos(952,890)}千緒的{\b0\bord8\fs150\c&HFCFDFE&\3c&H8900E1&\4c&HFEFFA6&}通學路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:04.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:06.69,qianxu-cut,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord1\shad1\blur10\fs60\c&HEDEEEA&\b1\4c&HB391D4&\3c&H967C82&\b1\pos(578,914)}柚「是你輸了哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.67,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想著你隔了好久終於聯繫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:08.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結果是問我借遊戲機
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:09.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是為了學習
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:11.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,理由就別問了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:14.70,qianxu-cut,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord5\shad10\blur10\fs60\c&HDEE3DB&\b1\4c&H3C2C28&\3c&H503251&\pos(912.667,908.667)}柚「從今天開始你就是我的東西了…沒問題吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 總感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:19.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是兩個大男人一起玩的遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.59,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像氛圍變得很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.07,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安 安藤大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:25.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:30.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:31.79,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:34.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我盯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:38.28,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,700)\bord0.1\shad8\blur6\4c&H6E61CD&\pos(1429.2,876.267)}與千緒決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.97,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是永平女學院的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:39.51,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是私立的超級大小姐學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:42.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種地方看到真是稀奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:44.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是沒睡醒吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:45.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 真的在的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:46.87,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:48.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}真的在的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:50.31,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}嗯 不過啊 那個啊 抓住了的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:51.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:52.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和我決鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:53.77,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:55.65,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 真的是猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:57.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在你家的屋頂上？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:58.67,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是兩隻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼樣的猴子你來模仿看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:07.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像和我爸有點像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:10.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:11.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:19.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:22.59,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 看起來挺強的一個已經被打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:24.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個就是你啦四眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才我提出決鬥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:29.97,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽你這麼一說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:31.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像剛才我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.09,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是對我們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:36.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖地把屁股靠過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:37.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要灌我腸嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.28,0:12:38.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\an7}註：此處的灌腸指日本小孩的一種惡作劇，基本等於千年殺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:38.19,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是灌腸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:39.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:43.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子是名校的學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:45.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要幹這種下流的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:46.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這該不會是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:51.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,決鬥乘上菊斗的某種有知性的情趣什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:51.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs65}註：此處的決鬥（けっとう）與菊斗（けつとう）諧音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:55.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個身法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:56.99,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你是菊斗經驗豐富的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:58.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然在說菊斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:02.71,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個四眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:08.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第二發要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:13.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:15.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然有使用者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:17.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Two Hand
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然攻擊回數和臂長有優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:24.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻是容易傷到手指的高風險姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.94,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,半吊子模仿這個的三班的高木
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:30.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把手指骨頭給折了的事情很有名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:31.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.51,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在哪裡學會的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:36.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,公立小學成長環境之差
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:38.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可別小看了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:41.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 你是這一塊的高手是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:44.51,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真有趣 明明只是個四眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:53.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:56.91,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回憶起以前被千緒幹得狼狽不堪的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:13:58.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.11,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:02.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先用在網上看到的方法把她給綁起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:03.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搬走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:05.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畫面很不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:10.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:12.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐 是時候告訴我們你的名字了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:15.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:18.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道你為什麼要突然朝我們撞上來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:21.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:24.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 只希望你告訴我這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:26.39,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是灌腸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:32.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要問力士為什麼要穿T字褲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:37.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:38.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:40.75,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.28,0:14:44.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒法原諒鮫島學園的女學生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:45.51,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:47.94,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為看起來很弱所以被我盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:49.31,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:55.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好像在裝逼說些讓人害臊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偷笑偷笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:59.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且還輸給了自己瞧不起的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:01.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:05.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺這孩子好像有點可怕啊 各種意義上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:08.07,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們倆已經沒法處理了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:08.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:11.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就用社會性制裁讓她哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:13.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是和學校聯繫對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:15.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後父母也會出現對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:16.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:19.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜你也去一趟醫院拿到診斷書
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:21.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 肛門科？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:25.47,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 尻山醫院是肛門科的醫院…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:26.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼有意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:36.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:39.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰輸給你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:42.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對於肩的柔軟程度我還是有自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:44.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還能戰鬥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:54.73,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢把真奈菜給…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:57.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狗屎四眼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:04.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我這就 送你和紮辮子的一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:10.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是 跑到公園的廣場出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.97,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你這麼點也足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:13.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暫停
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:18.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的氣勢哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:23.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在公園要安靜點 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:28.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁著氣勢 跑到別人面前了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:31.47,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣冷靜地想一下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:35.01,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和女孩子在認真地玩灌腸合戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:38.31,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊 翹起屁屁 讓我手指進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:39.11,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有案件？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.21,0:16:41.79,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只會覺得我們是很糟糕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:45.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把她手指綁起來對形象也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:47.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.34,0:16:48.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這麼情緒高漲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:50.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:52.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:54.05,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣配合著她後退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:56.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是社交舞蹈的練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:57.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:16:59.91,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 拉開一定距離了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帶到樹林裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:04.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,插她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:12.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:14.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 管理的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:18.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要修剪得這麼不徹底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:21.59,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自爆了呢 現在就給你最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:26.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最後 能不能 告訴我你的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.54,0:17:28.51,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:33.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目的是 報大哥的仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:40.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我 你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久志取前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:44.27,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:46.71,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被女性的悲鳴所吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:48.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.31,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是女性的悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:51.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在做卡巴迪的自主練習的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到了好像很愉悅的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:58.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來這個公園 好像是前輩隱居的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:03.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到會找到這麼可愛的小兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:07.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要往你菊花來一發
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.13,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:16.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個屁股是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:23.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我用手指插入過無數個屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:26.87,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼說 總好像有什麼不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:31.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果手指進入了這個屁股的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:34.91,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就會變成不是菊斗的其他什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:36.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你發覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:44.19,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女人的身體是不能隨意傷害或者被傷害的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:46.53,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女人是該保養的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:47.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,令人憐愛的少女喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:50.59,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:55.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為女士 要保有自覺成為大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:59.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能沉迷於這種下流的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:02.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:12.53,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋 笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:16.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你和那個孩子是什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不認識她 突然就被襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:22.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那還真是災難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:24.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也要去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:25.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:28.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧前輩 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.52,0:19:31.31,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:33.79,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個小鬼 絕對要殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.65,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把她屁股插到我手臂為止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:39.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直接給她做盲腸手術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.54,0:19:41.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 怎麼辦好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:44.75,qianxu-cut,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\xshad5\yshad5\bord3\fs120\c&H9982EF&\3c&HFEFEFE&\4c&HCBE5FC&\pos(990,892)}千緒的{\b0\fs150\bord8\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H9982EE&\4c&HCBE5FD&}通學路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:50.11,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好恨 我好恨那個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.75,0:19:51.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不坐下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:52.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:54.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,午飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.74,0:19:55.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不餓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:57.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見到她的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:19:59.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.27,0:20:01.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜 去不去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:04.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對要殺了…去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:05.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真靈巧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:12.88,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,0)\bord0.1\shad8\blur6\4c&H6E61CD&\pos(1521.2,884.267)}那一天的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:12.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:16.82,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個老婆婆 最近一直坐在那裡對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:19.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像一直低著頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:24.39,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 我爸爸說過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:27.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個老婆婆坐著的對面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.90,0:20:30.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,深處有一座盛開著漂亮的紫陽花的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:37.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:37.87,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:43.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們一直都健康的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:46.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要每年都來看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:48.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:52.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後失去了丈夫的現在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:55.47,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尋找著那個模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:21:02.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻被與那些人的回憶無關的現代社會遮蓋了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:05.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用鐵 混凝土和玻璃的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:08.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在誰都沒注意到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:15.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.08,0:21:17.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的話 和我們聊聊吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:22.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:24.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡那裡那裡就那裡…就是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:27.39,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 連擊斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:32.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你別坐那蹭店裡的wifi啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你好多次了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.95,0:21:36.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不想說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:38.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這是給客人們用的設備
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:40.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾也到裡面點杯咖啡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:43.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 下地獄去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:47.07,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:50.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要設定屏蔽你的終端了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:54.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種東西 看我黑進去突破給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:57.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傻逼傻逼傻逼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還會來的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,----EDCN------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:21.95,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}回家路上說點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.25,0:22:25.41,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}就這麼投入其中的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:28.70,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}在好像很長的這一小段時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:31.94,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}內心深處便會怦然一動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:35.26,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}雖然是理所當然的見面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:38.57,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}但是每天卻非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:45.23,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}歡笑的時候 生氣的時候 都想全力碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.27,0:22:51.04,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}不想說再見的感覺是想要隱藏起來的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.42,0:22:57.21,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}在回家之前就是上學哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:22:59.42,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}明天再見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:04.24,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}不是你的話不就開始不了不是嗎 你說對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.58,0:23:10.66,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}無法見面的時間 為什麼總是感覺有所欠缺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.87,0:23:12.71,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}明天再見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.79,0:23:17.66,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}和你一起的話無聊的一天也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.94,0:23:21.25,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}一如既往的景色 就由我們來破壞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.39,0:23:25.07,qianxu_EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,500)}然後循環現在七色之路
Comment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:00.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,----EDJP-------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:21.95,qianxu_EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}帰り道は何を話そう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.25,0:22:25.41,qianxu_EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(100,300)}なんとなくに身を任せたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.58,0:22:28.70,qianxu_EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}長いようで短い時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:31.94,qianxu_EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}胸の奥がきゅっとなるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.07,0:22:35.26,qianxu_EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}当たり前に会えるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:38.57,qianxu_EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}毎日が楽しすぎるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.86,0:22:45.23,qianxu_EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}笑う時も　怒る時も　全力でぶつかってたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.27,0:22:51.04,qianxu_EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}さよならしたくない感じは隠していたい感じ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.42,0:22:57.21,qianxu_EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}おうちに帰るまでが通学だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:22:59.42,qianxu_EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}また明日ね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:04.24,qianxu_EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur4\fad(10,300)}君じゃなきゃ始まらないじゃない そうでしょう
